title: Recruiting players for Ranked Team Gold +
body:
Gold supp main looking to make a flex Team / Group.  Must be gold +. Games will be around weekdays 7pm till 10pm NZT but can be fluid to suit the team. Possibly on weekends too but hours will be whatever suits the team. Looking for serious players who want to practice learn and develop as a team.
Add me in game (Onceorthrice) or leave a comment.

So far Have got myself for support a jung/adc player and a top/mid player. Also keen for a few casuals / subs to fill.
